snippet.title: Delta0: A puzzle game to stimulate your brain!
snippet.description:
Delta0: A puzzle game to stimulate your brain!

Delta0 pronounced "Delta-Zero" is available on Android, iOS, Windows, Linux, macOS, Steam, Amazon Fire, Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and other web browsers.

Release Date: December 1, 2020

Website: https://www.delta0.link/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1424570/Delta0/
https://www.jsr-productions.com/
